Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕參考自：KTXP，Airota，AME，Suzu-Kaze，HYSUB字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別感謝KTXP，Airota，AME，Suzu-Kaze，HYSUB，CASO & SGS 諸位字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------三次元去死線：刪除一生沒戀人T─T---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界為子宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子宮即是死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切事物——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在誕生之前就已經腐爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓界隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從本部傳來聯絡  人體基因調整實驗體XC21逃進了我們的轄區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令書
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽古典音樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怎麼聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調和有著無上的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成千上萬的音符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個地被安排在它應該出現的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一絲紊亂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標攜帶傳染性病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標與其接觸者全部予以燒毀處置…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今哪還有什麼無法控制的病原體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想保護機密而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  處置是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是燒毀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和諧的音符只有被消除而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不懂忍耐的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝扮跟通緝令一樣才比較容易找到達特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(912,661)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是更容易被找到才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  德魯德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs-3}德魯德——\N出自狄更斯晚年未完稿的小說\N《艾德溫･德魯德之謎 The Mystery of Edwin Drood》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德魯德？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這腐敗封閉的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一還沒有劃上句點的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然還有閒工夫撿流浪犬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實牠親近的反而是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別這樣  狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐的王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連撫摸小狗的頭都沒辦法的「彌達斯之手」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs-3}彌達斯——\N希臘神話中能點石成金的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象憑目測迴避子彈  向海岸方向逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能為生物兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一名隊員被目擊遭傳染性病毒的攻擊而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複  對象可能為生物兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就用「那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那個」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東邊山麓α3位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜點  狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丟了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才的報告  我聽到的就是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標故意在顯眼的地方等候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引誘End Rave出動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知為何隱藏行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是造船廠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於達特來說這陷阱也太過簡單了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(459,661)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對追捕你的End Rave進行反追蹤並跟到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就生物兵器而言  還真是有趣的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算你能躲過一發子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數量應該是不可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在你死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人不知道達特的事喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(694,661)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達特？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(622,661)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  也不可能說個再見就能走人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  史庫路奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(682,661)}Scrooge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs-3}史庫路奇——\N出自狄更斯小說《聖誕頌歌 A Christmas Carol》\N埃比･尼澤史庫路奇是個守財奴,但從一夜的奇特經\N歷,從吝嗇鬼變成一個仁厚､寬容而熱情的慈善家。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你渴求的  你的黃金取出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…世界還未完全調和嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德魯德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  那就是王之能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  史庫路奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在安慰我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是為了戲弄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻狗脖子上有手術過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對王之手有反應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是被植入了人類基因組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個…好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵的裡面在孕育著卵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的雛鳥們在重演著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何東西留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這具腐爛的屍骸
